remove_gui_marker(25.10)                              remove_gui_marker(25.10)

Name
       remove_gui_marker - Removes a marker from the design layout

Syntax
       remove_gui_marker

       [-help]

       {-name <string> | -all }

       Removes a marker from the design layout.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs the command usage and a brief description about the com-
              mand parameters.

       -name <string>
              Specifies  the  name of the marker to be removed from the design
              layout.

       -all   Removes all markers from the design layout.

Related Information
              * add_gui_marker

              * list_gui_marker

